                </div>
                <div class="fld-container">
                    <div class="fld-header">
                       <span class="fld-title">Seeking Collaborators For</span>
                    </div>
                    <div id="piphs-fld4" class="fld-value" style="display:none">Ideas or areas for further research exploration. Can include what potential funding might support these ideas.</div>
                </div>
                <div class="fld-container">
                    <div class="fld-header">
                       <span class="fld-title">Future Project Ideas</span>
                    </div>
                    <div id="piphs-fld5" class="fld-value" style="display:none">Ideas or areas for further research exploration. Can include what potential funding might support these ideas.</div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        ]]></Content>
</Module>